gameobjects.dungeon

Class Tunnel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameobjects.UniqueObject
      • gameobjects.Itemholder
        • gameobjects.dungeon.Tunnel

  • public class Tunnel
extends Itemholder
    The basic block from which the dungeon is build. Can contain actors and items. Knows the blocks that are next to it. Is an ItemHolder.
